    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the albuterol thing sounds okay, but i dont really wanna go to the clinic right now, the wait times are huge. if i just increase my current inhaler usage bit by bit every day, like an extra puff every morning, would that be enough to manage it? i dont want to make it a big deal if it's just my age catching up.",
